label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"鸡螨虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡螨虫，Dermanyssus gallinae，属节肢动物门蛛形纲蜱螨目皮刺科、皮刺螨属的一类螨虫。

label: [{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"鸡血","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"鸡痘病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":36,"end":39,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"大肠杆菌","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 体形微小，主要靠吸食鸡血为生，有时也吸人血，通过叮咬鸡体可传播鸡痘病毒、新城疫、大肠杆菌等。

label: [{"start":1,"end":2,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"商品蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"种鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"鸡刺皮螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"林禽刺螨","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 对鸡（尤其商品蛋鸡和种鸡）危害较大的2种，即鸡刺皮螨和林禽刺螨。

label: [{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"疥癣虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"鸡螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"鸡膝螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"脱羽螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":35,"end":40,"text":"鸡突变膝螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"鳞足螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"红螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":49,"end":52,"text":"梄架蜻","labels":["disease"]},{"start":54,"end":59,"text":"鸡新勋痒螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":60,"end":65,"text":"鸡奇棒痒螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 简介：螨俗称疥癣虫，鸡螨有20余种，对鸡危害严重的有鸡膝螨(脱羽螨)、鸡突变膝螨(鳞足螨)、红螨(梄架蜻)、鸡新勋痒螨(鸡奇棒痒螨)等。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"鸡螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"羽毛根部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":19,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"脚","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"鳞片内层","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡螨寄生在鸡的皮肤、羽毛根部或潜伏在腿脚无毛的鳞片内层，以吸血为生。

label: [{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"鸡螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"贫血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"死亡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 当鸡螨大量繁衍滋生时，可引起鸡贫血甚至死亡。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"鸡螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"土鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"体表寄生虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡螨是土鸡放养过程常见的体表寄生虫病，特别在阴暗、潮湿的饲养场较多见。

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"鸡螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"鸡只","labels":["type"]}]
text: 发病特点：鸡螨一般白天寄居于鸡舍的墙缝、鸡笼及笼架的缝隙和食槽、水管夹缝等处，夜间侵袭鸡只吸血。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"肛门","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"腹部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 螨虫主要集中在鸡体的肛门周围、腹部。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"笼养鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"平养鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 笼养鸡发生严重，容易被发现。平养鸡也有发生。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":29,"text":"在晚上对鸡体进行检查","labels":["control"]}]
text: 螨虫白天隐藏在地板条下或隐秘的地方，应在晚上对鸡体进行检查才可发现。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 螨虫的传播途径有工具、工人、老鼠、苍蝇。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":18,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"腹","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"胸","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"翅膀","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":29,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":31,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":33,"text":"背","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"血液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":43,"end":46,"text":"组织液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":54,"end":55,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"皮肤红肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":57,"end":59,"text":"红肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"损伤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":62,"end":66,"text":"继发炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":77,"end":79,"text":"不安","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":92,"end":94,"text":"消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":90,"end":94,"text":"鸡体消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":95,"end":97,"text":"贫血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":98,"end":102,"text":"生长缓慢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":90,"end":92,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":76,"end":77,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 症状：螨虫寄生有全身性，寄生在鸡的腿、腹、胸、翅膀内侧、头、颈、背等处，吸食鸡体血液和组织液，并分泌毒素引发鸡皮肤红肿、损伤继发炎症，反复侵袭、骚扰引起鸡不安，影响采食和休息，导致鸡体消瘦、贫血、生长缓慢，严重影响上市品质。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"鸡刺皮螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"鸡刺皮螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"红螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"栖架螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"鸡血","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 分类：鸡刺皮螨，鸡刺皮螨又叫红螨、栖架螨，主要寄居于鸡和家禽的生活环境中，为夜间活动虫体白天不易发现主要吸食鸡血，有时也吸人血。

label: [{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"鸡皮刺螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"鸡皮刺螨","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 生活发育史：鸡皮刺螨的发育史为卵—幼虫—第一期若虫—第二期若虫—成虫鸡皮刺螨主要生活在鸡舍的笼具料槽上。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 螨虫没有明显的季节性只要温度适应一年四季都会有，但是在干燥的环境下容易死亡。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"鸡皮刺螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"鸡血","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"贫血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"降蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":38,"end":44,"text":"抗体水平下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"瘙痒不安","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":82,"end":87,"text":"家禽传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":32,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":45,"end":46,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 危害：鸡皮刺螨繁殖速度快，且每个繁殖过程都会大量吸食鸡血，造成鸡贫血、降蛋、抗体水平下降、鸡瘙痒不安、浪费饲料营养，造成养殖户的养殖成本上升，生产效益下降，同时传播家禽传染病。

label: [{"start":45,"end":53,"text":"涂刷或喷洒于鸡体","labels":["control"]},{"start":59,"end":65,"text":"药液喷洒鸡舍","labels":["control"]},{"start":74,"end":85,"text":"房舍可用石灰水粉刷消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":14,"text":"蝇毒磷水乳剂","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":24,"text":"敌百虫溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":38,"end":43,"text":"敌杀死溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":78,"end":81,"text":"石灰水","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 防治：0.03%蝇毒磷水乳剂或0.5%敌百虫溶液或每干克水中加50～80毫克敌杀死溶液，可涂刷或喷洒于鸡体，同时用上述药液喷洒鸡舍、鸡窝和墙壁缝隙，房舍可用石灰水粉刷消毒；因为这些药用药多年，已产生抗药性，而且无法杀死虫卵。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"林禽刺螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"北方羽螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"鸡刺皮螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":43,"end":44,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 林禽刺螨：也叫北方羽螨，成虫呈长椭圆形，形态与鸡刺皮螨相似，但背板呈纺锤形。雌虫产卵于鸡的羽毛上，1天内孵化为幼虫。

label: [{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]}]
text: 幼虫和两个若虫期在4天之内发育完成，从幼虫孵化到成虫产卵的生活史均在鸡体上。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"林禽刺螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"羽毛变黑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"变黑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":36,"text":"肛门周围皮肤结痂龟裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"结痂龟裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"肛门周围皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 林禽刺螨伏在鸡体上昼夜吸血，严重感染时可使羽毛变黑，肛门周围皮肤结痂龟裂。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"产蛋量减少","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"饲料消耗增加","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"鸡体贫血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"贫血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"死亡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"鸡体","labels":["type"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"林禽刺螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"鸡痘","labels":["disease"]},{"start":52,"end":55,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 受感染的鸡群产蛋量减少，饲料消耗增加，感染严重的，可造成鸡体贫血，甚至死亡。此外，林禽刺螨还可能是鸡痘和新城疫的传播媒介。

label: [{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"药浴","labels":["control"]},{"start":30,"end":47,"text":"将药液喷洒于鸡舍内及笼架等饲养设备","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"敌百虫溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":25,"text":"三氯杀螨醇溶液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 防治：用0.1%敌百虫溶液或0.2%三氯杀螨醇溶液药浴，然后将药液喷洒于鸡舍内及笼架等饲养设备。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"脱羽膝螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":36,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":36,"end":44,"text":"自己啄掉大片羽毛","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"引起剧烈瘙痒","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"羽毛根部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 脱羽膝螨：寄生在鸡羽毛根部，成虫形态呈球形。寄生部位引起剧烈瘙痒，以致鸡自己啄掉大片羽毛。危害多在夏季。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"鸡脱羽膝螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"林禽刺螨","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 防治：鸡脱羽膝螨的防治方法与林禽刺螨相同。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"鸡突变膝螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"鳞足螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 鸡突变膝螨：也叫鳞足螨，常寄生于年龄较大的鸡。虫体几乎呈球形，表皮上具有明显的条纹。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"突变膝螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":8,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"脚","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"鳞片","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"患部发炎","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 突变膝螨寄生在鸡腿脚的鳞片，并在患部深层产卵繁殖，整个生活史不离开患部，使患部发炎。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"先起鳞片","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":18,"text":"皮肤增生而变粗糙","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"裂缝","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":29,"text":"流出大量渗出液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"增生","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"变粗糙","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 病患处先起鳞片，接着皮肤增生而变粗糙，裂缝，流出大量渗出液。

label: [{"start":0,"end":10,"text":"干燥后形成白色的痂皮","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":38,"text":"寄图30突变膝螨生虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"鸡石灰脚","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 干燥后形成白色的痂皮，好像涂上一层石灰的样子，因而这种寄图30突变膝螨生虫病又叫鸡石灰脚。

label: [{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":23,"text":"趾骨坏死而发生畸形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"畸形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"趾骨","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"鸡只","labels":["type"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"行走困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":37,"end":43,"text":"产蛋都受影响","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 如不及时治疗，可引起关节炎，趾骨坏死而发生畸形，鸡只行走困难，采食、生长、产蛋都受影响。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡鳞足螨","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":18,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 鸡鳞足螨的感染力不强，通常是一部分鸡受害较严重。

label: [{"start":4,"end":15,"text":"将病鸡脚泡人温肥皂水中","labels":["control"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"除去痂皮","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"涂上","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":8,"text":"脚","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"肥皂水","labels":["drug"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"硫黄软膏","labels":["drug"]},{"start":41,"end":46,"text":"石炭酸软膏","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 防治：先将病鸡脚泡人温肥皂水中，使痂皮泡软，除去痂皮，涂上20%硫黄软膏或2010石炭酸软膏，每天2次，连用3-5天。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"鸡脚","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":17,"text":"敌百虫溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":22,"end":29,"text":"三氯杀螨醇溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":57,"end":59,"text":"药液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":80,"end":82,"text":"药浴","labels":["control"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"刮去结痂","labels":["control"]},{"start":49,"end":55,"text":"用小刷子刷脚","labels":["control"]}]
text: 也可将鸡脚浸泡在0.1%敌百虫溶液或0.2%三氯杀螨醇溶液中4-5分钟，一面用小）9刮去结痂，一面用小刷子刷脚，使药液渗入组织内以杀死虫体。间隔2—3周后，可再药浴1次。

label: [{"start":5,"end":17,"text":"保持圈舍和环境的清洁卫生","labels":["control"]},{"start":18,"end":24,"text":"定期清理粪便","labels":["control"]},{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"清除杂草","labels":["control"]},{"start":38,"end":46,"text":"粪便集中堆肥发酵","labels":["control"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"螨虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":56,"end":65,"text":"定期使用杀虫剂预防","labels":["control"]},{"start":60,"end":63,"text":"杀虫剂","labels":["drug"]},{"start":75,"end":78,"text":"辛硫磷","labels":["drug"]},{"start":69,"end":70,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":69,"end":90,"text":"鸡出栏后使用辛硫磷对圈舍和运动场地全面喷洒","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":37,"text":"堵塞墙缝","labels":["control"]}]
text: 预防：1、保持圈舍和环境的清洁卫生，定期清理粪便，清除杂草、污物，堵塞墙缝，粪便集中堆肥发酵等，以减少螨虫数量；定期使用杀虫剂预防，一般在鸡出栏后使用辛硫磷对圈舍和运动场地全面喷洒，间隔10天左右再喷洒1次。

label: [{"start":9,"end":27,"text":"新老鸡群分隔饲养严格执行全进全出制度","labels":["control"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"避免混养","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":39,"text":"严格卫生检疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":40,"end":48,"text":"发现感染及时诊治","labels":["control"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 2、防止交叉感染，新老鸡群分隔饲养严格执行全进全出制度，避免混养，严格卫生检疫，发现感染及时诊治。

label: [{"start":0,"end":11,"text":"注意新老鸡群的隔离饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":12,"end":17,"text":"建立隔离带","labels":["control"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 注意新老鸡群的隔离饲养，建立隔离带，防止交叉感染。

label: [{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"拌料内服","labels":["control"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"伊维菌素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"阿维菌素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"感染鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 3、感染鸡群的治疗可用阿维菌素、伊维菌素等拌料内服，用量为每千克饲料用0.15～0.2克。

label: [{"start":1,"end":4,"text":"商品鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":12,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"灭虫菊酯","labels":["drug"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"碳酸软膏","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"沙浴法","labels":["control"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"药浴法","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":33,"text":"个体局部涂抹","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":14,"text":"用灭虫菊酯带鸡喷雾","labels":["control"]}]
text: 对商品鸡可用灭虫菊酯带鸡喷雾，也可使用沙浴法、药浴法或个体局部涂抹2%的碳酸软膏等。
